mhdir
======
An `mh <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/MH_Message_Handling_System>`_-style
interface to maildirs

References

* `MH & nmh: Email for Users & Programmers <http://rand-mh.sourceforge.net/>`_
* The `mailbox <https://docs.python.org/3.5/library/mailbox.html>`_ package is
  hard-coded for maildirs with ``.``-terminated prefixes. And the package
  doesn't do much overall.
* `offlineimap <http://offlineimap.org/documentation.html>`_

Much of the documentation and function signatures are copied from nmh.
